{
  "entries": [
    {
      "offset": "0x18ab04",
      "back_en": "He must be inviting those closest to my",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'dear' não traduzido, mas continua na linha seguinte."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18ab33",
      "back_en": "brother... to convince them to become his",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'beguile' suavizado p/ 'convencer', aceitável."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18ae51",
      "back_en": "General Mikazuchi has been enemy of my",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'enemy' antecipado da próxima linha; sentido mantido."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18ae80",
      "back_en": "brother for years... If you falter, he will",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Reestruturação entre linhas; OK no conjunto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18af12",
      "back_en": "waiting for you... Please, come in.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18b173",
      "back_en": "you dead-on/right on.",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'em cheio' não traduz 'in full'; usar 'integralmente'."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18b2b7",
      "back_en": "A guest that not even Mikazuchi can refuse...?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18b384",
      "back_en": "Mikazuchi. I can guarantee their credibility...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18b44d",
      "back_en": "Hm. Guests for you? What a big surprise.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Idiomatismo equivalente."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18b4a9",
      "back_en": "So this must be the other guest. Who could it",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18b4da",
      "back_en": "be if he were talking to Mikazuchi so casually?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18b535",
      "back_en": "I caused. We shall leave at once.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'may have' perdido; 'na mesma hora' = at once OK."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18b560",
      "back_en": "I don't mind. By all means, let them in.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'Por todos os meios' é calque um pouco artificial."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18b597",
      "back_en": "These guests have piqued my interest. Don't...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Continuação; OK."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18b6e1",
      "back_en": "He is more merciful than Lord Mikazuchi...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18b751",
      "back_en": "I appreciate your coming.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18b984",
      "back_en": "Lord Raiko!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18b9bf",
      "back_en": "with the brilliant strategies!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18ba9c",
      "back_en": "You would be... Oshtor's younger sister, then?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18bb03",
      "back_en": "few people should know...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18bb98",
      "back_en": "Then how does this guy know she's Oshtor's sister?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Acrescenta 'irmã' e '?'; sentido OK."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18bc81",
      "back_en": "I have known for some time that that girl",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18bcb1",
      "back_en": "is Oshtor's sister.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'sibling' especificado p/ irmã; OK no contexto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18bcc6",
      "back_en": "And I also know that—",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18bcf5",
      "back_en": "That you, Haku, work undercover as agent",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'de Oshtor' segue na próxima; OK."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18bd23",
      "back_en": "of Oshtor, and perform tasks that he cannot publicly",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18bd56",
      "back_en": "support (noun).",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'apoio' (subst.) deveria ser verbo 'apoiar' (não pode apoiar publicamente)."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18be88",
      "back_en": "allow me to make a proper introduction.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18bf1c",
      "back_en": "Eight Pillar Generals. And also—",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18bf7a",
      "back_en": "I am the brother of Mikazuchi.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18c1f9",
      "back_en": "The man does have a tendency to trust others",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18c228",
      "back_en": "easily, but it is rare indeed for him to trust fully",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18c298",
      "back_en": "For him to trust a man like you...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'rely on'→'confiar' aceitável."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18c2f9",
      "back_en": "Who exactly are you?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18c34b",
      "back_en": "You met while Oshtor was traveling as Ukon,",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18c40f",
      "back_en": "out of nowhere one day, with no past to speak of.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'do nada'='out of the blue'; OK."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18c43b",
      "back_en": "Who are you...?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18c619",
      "back_en": "...Yes. I was close by and thought I'd see",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18c648",
      "back_en": "my poor irresponsible brother,",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'check in with' implícito; 'reprobate'→'irresponsável' OK."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18c711",
      "back_en": "Farewell.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18cfdd",
      "back_en": "...Prize?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'Prêmio'≈'reward'; 'recompensa' seria mais exato."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18d09a",
      "back_en": "...Miruhj.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18d27f",
      "back_en": "Don't you (pl) think it beautiful?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18d415",
      "back_en": "Sounds like somebody's mouth is watering.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18d5f2",
      "back_en": "My dear brother brought me some. They are made",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18d78a",
      "back_en": "laugh of a fierce predator toying with its prey.",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'leer' (olhar maldoso) virou 'riso' (riso); mudou o sentido."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18d7f4",
      "back_en": "her trapped in Mikazuchi's gaze.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18d815",
      "back_en": "Eat.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18d81a",
      "back_en": "What's wrong? You don't want any?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18d8ce",
      "back_en": "*Malicious smile*...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'Smirk' adaptado; OK."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18d921",
      "back_en": "He's gotta have some ulterior motive!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18d947",
      "back_en": "Why so modest? Eat.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18d979",
      "back_en": "It was the perfect opportunity.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18d9fa",
      "back_en": "feast...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18da30",
      "back_en": "and this is our last meal...!?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18da4f",
      "back_en": "Then Nekone was right all along...!?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18da74",
      "back_en": "Wh-What... What exactly are you... plotting...?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18daa4",
      "back_en": "...Hm? I have no idea what you mean.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18daff",
      "back_en": "what your plan is!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18db44",
      "back_en": "You intend to use them to try to win me over!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18dbd0",
      "back_en": "isn't it!?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Tag question equivalente."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18dc0e",
      "back_en": "into his trap.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18dd16",
      "back_en": "Hah... Worry not, child. I'm not planning",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18dd42",
      "back_en": "anything of the sort. Nothing... absolutely... nothing.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18ddea",
      "back_en": "You could say... I wanted tea.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18de73",
      "back_en": "Which is why I wished to have tea with you.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18df80",
      "back_en": "What else would I have invited you (pl) for?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18e044",
      "back_en": "would have felt something more sinister...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18e0ac",
      "back_en": "The way I see it, he's up to no good.",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'However you look at this' (qualquer ângulo) virou 'Do jeito que vejo' (minha visão)."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18e41c",
      "back_en": "Mmph--! This floury texture is interesting...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'crumbly'→'farinhosa'; efeito boca-cheia mantido."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18e639",
      "back_en": "...S-So that is the fabled--",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18e7e3",
      "back_en": "Remember, it could be... poisoned!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18e89f",
      "back_en": "nothing goes untasted. If I die, I die for science!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18e972",
      "back_en": "Wh-What!? Was it REALLY poisoned!?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'venenada' está errado; correto 'envenenada'."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18ecfe",
      "back_en": "I-It... I don't recall asking for his help.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Faltam acentos (Não/recordo); sentido OK."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18ed8e",
      "back_en": "Urgh... A-Are you threatening me?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Faltam acentos; sentido OK."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18f6ae",
      "back_en": "might actually be a real nice guy.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18f721",
      "back_en": "This man is my dear brother's...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Frase truncada mantida com placeholder; OK."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18f8be",
      "back_en": "we could be...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18f979",
      "back_en": "I get it now! He's just...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18fa1b",
      "back_en": "to end the sentence with 'in strangling her'.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'wring her neck'→'estrangulá-la' aceitável."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18fa79",
      "back_en": "everything I said! You are not to be trusted!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x18fabd",
      "back_en": "...This is absolutely hopeless.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    }
  ],
  "reviewed": 83
}